title: Klovn til kaffen
overview: Six historic Norwegian comedians sit down together and talk about humour and how it shaped them.In season one we follow Espen Eckbo, Hege Schøyen, Linn Skåber, Knut Lystad, Stein Johan «Steinjo» Grieg Halvorsen and Odd-Magnus Williamson.In season two we follow Bård Tufte Johansen, Trond Fausa Aurvåg, Calle Hellevang-Larsen, Anne Marit Jacobsen, Cecilie Steinmann Neess, Nils Vogt.
